Class Matches

java.lang.Object
  |
  +--com.vividsolutions.jcs.conflate.roads.Matches
public class Matches
extends java.lang.Object

Maintains a set of matches of one object to other ones. Matches are ordered by a real-valued value. The ordering can either be increasing or decreasing. Matches can be accessed either by the matched object or by the sorted values of the matches.
